vocaloid is a voice synthesizer program where you basically input phonemes and the computer sings them. different companies have created different "characters" for said program, one of which, Miku Hatsune, is the most famous. she definitely looks like an anime character, but she is just a virtual idol that anyone can make sing anything. there are plenty of other singers that can sing in a bunch of different languages too, and they all have different appearances and voices!! there are other voice synth programs and well-known vsingers from them too, such as Elanore Forte from SynthV and Kasane Teto from Utau, but vocaloid and ofc Miku remain the most well known
